{"word":"παλαίω","slug":"παλαίω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παλαίω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>πάλη</el>\n<p/><i>to wrestle</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>: <el>π. τινί</el> <i>to wrestle with</i> one, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>παλαισθείς</el> <i>beaten</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/>"}]}